ColourTrans_SetoppTextColour  (&40762)
#Parent ColourTrans_
=>	R0 =	<palette entry=>colourtrans_paletteentry>
	R3 =	flags:	bit 7 set for background, else foreground
	 	  	other bits 0 (reserved)
   
<=	R0 =	GCOL
	R3 preserved

This call, given a palette entry, works out the furthest GCOL in the current mode and palette, and sets the text colour to it.
#Line
See <PRM 3, page 396=>PRM-3:396>.
